{"tid":1082522,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈要求紅十字會應尊重捐血者的意願","createTime":"2019-03-29T04:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T15:56:08.000Z","uid":4528,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ef015c3a739e73389e8317178b4c0efedafc6c07","tid":1082522,"uid":4528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:22:38.000Z","msg":"建議紅十字會應讓捐血者選擇捐血的去處<br />\n姐係選擇公立醫院/私家醫院<br />\n如果私家醫院唔願意承擔輸血所衍生嘅成本<br />\n我可以選擇唔捐血俾私家醫院<br />\n我係極不滿私家醫院用我的血去賺錢<br />\n佢最後係其他手術收返錢係另一回事<br />\n我相信當有得選擇時 大部分人選擇公立醫院<br />\n可以迫使私家醫院免收輸血的費用"},{"pid":"fb0d947d78b807796c656c3dbe0f97059f38c012","tid":1082522,"uid":28574,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:26:17.000Z","msg":"啱，都係唔捐血了"},{"pid":"bf46dbcdea499eea48b358dbdd2f82f9edfb5920","tid":1082522,"uid":21267,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"流落海都唔撚益紅十"},{"pid":"1cf5c09839574426609630725dfe55c272448732","tid":1082522,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:34:35.000Z","msg":"點解連登咁撚on9，每隔一排就有人反紅十字會，但係講野從來唔會俾證據，完全係空口講白話"},{"pid":"19be626ad4c488d00d52bc0be445ab1f2d05ebc2","tid":1082522,"uid":4528,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:35:02.000Z","msg":"我次撚次都捐最撚大包450ML<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗到私家醫院輸血都要收錢 正仆街<br />\n有本事醫院自己做d血出去輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02d1bae4b94e10ba6705d956089643299a6f311","tid":1082522,"uid":4528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:41:15.000Z","msg":"支持私家醫院自行向市民買血<br />\n你賣幾多錢我唔會理"},{"pid":"d45ac2f606289e9c5c9c9625657c291f0ca650db","tid":1082522,"uid":4528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1cf5c09839574426609630725dfe55c272448732","tid":1082522,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:34:35.000Z","msg":"點解連登咁撚on9，每隔一排就有人反紅十字會，但係講野從來唔會俾證據，完全係空口講白話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:53:54.000Z","msg":"私家醫院輸血收錢要咩證據呀 <br />\n係咪要貼個收費表出黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20170506/56658567\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170506%2F56658567&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HSwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=8433ccac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170506%2F56658567&h=d2400d68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20170506/56658567</a><br />\n<br />\n私家醫院擺明係無錢就唔會醫<br />\n淨係依個理由我都唔想捐俾佢喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07217072a1a38e8e3359229df810ed0f4ec6e3aa","tid":1082522,"uid":178552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:19:42.000Z","msg":"仲有想知捐完幾時同咩事用咗<br />\n捐完好似倒咗落海攞嚟輸咗比蝗大肚婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1d56a09906ca397ae06e397005e54c114daa15","tid":1082522,"uid":245644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T15:54:15.000Z","msg":"唔會捐，身邊識的人聽完我講，都決定唔捐了"},{"pid":"c93c74eb016586ddf71d548ebf422f13a52f4352","tid":1082522,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T15:56:08.000Z","msg":"紅十字會謀取暴利， 用香港人的血賣俾大陸人， 可恥"}]}